'''mc chris''' is a 33 year old [[wigger]] from Libertyville (a.k.a. Shitertyville),Illinois, (the existence of the town has been refuted by many Scholars, and has [[some argue|yet to be]] [[fact|proven]]).  With his dulcet tones of a [[13 year old boy]], it has been said that listening to his music is worse than [[Dianne Thorley|being raped by over 9,000 Arabs]]. His songs consist of his claimed [[nerd]] [[street cred|roots]], like playing [[video games]] and reading [[comic books]].  His hobbies include bragging and singing about how much he loves [[weed]], bitching about how much his life sucks on [[Facebook]] and flirting with [[16 year old girls]] on [[MySpace]]. 

