==Adult Swim==
[[File:Mc_chris_hates_emos.jpg|thumb|mc chris is a known [[emo]] hater.]]
MC used to work at [[Adult Swim]] but quit so he could shit out music at a more rapid rate. He is also MC [[Watersports|Pee Pants]], on ''[[Aqua Teen Hunger Force]]''. MC, also appropriately, did the voice of Hesh, a cracked-out mongoloid on ''Sealab 2021''. More recently mc chris is in talks with his former employer for an mc chris cartoon, which official sources say will consist of two separate 15 minute commercials of his [[Ebay]] store which will play 3 times a night, 7 nights a week on [[Cartoon Network]].

